=Episode 9=
=Crisis &amp; Proposal=

11
00:00:53,790 --> 00:00:54,880
What's on your mind now?

12
00:00:57,710 --> 00:00:59,560
Jiang Niannian asked about Jiang Xiaodi.

13
00:01:03,110 --> 00:01:04,230
You didn't tell her, did you?

14
00:01:06,510 --> 00:01:07,430
You owe me one.

15
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,000
When you have time,

16
00:01:09,590 --> 00:01:10,710
