17
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,040
Haven't you studied me enough?

18
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,870
Now I'm your lab rat too?

19
00:01:21,430 --> 00:01:22,310
If you say no,

20
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,070
I'll dissect her instead.

21
00:01:25,070 --> 00:01:27,150
Her bone structure is excellent.

22
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,840
She's worth my time.

23
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,760
I'm warning you one last time.

24
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,040
Don't you touch her.

25
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:40,070
If you love her so much,

26
