39
00:02:14,190 --> 00:02:15,630
(Zhong Minghui is already detained.)

40
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,680
(Liu Yexi can't do much now.)

41
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,590
(As long as Xiaodi's surgery succeeds...)

42
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:28,150
You

43
00:02:28,710 --> 00:02:29,560
were waiting for me?

44
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:35,190
Hey, handsome,

45
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:36,680
mind giving me a ride?

46
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,240
My honor.

47
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,960
- Ye Lang.
- Mm.

48
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:01,580
Are you close with Dr. Zheng?

49
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,590
