Which hospital is he in now?

57
00:03:23,830 --> 00:03:24,680
Dr. Zheng

58
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:26,520
is the best neurosurgeon in Manlong.

59
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,520
Wanna transfer him here?

60
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,840
He's with relatives,

61
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:33,870
