62
00:03:34,060 --> 00:03:34,960
No need to bother you.

63
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,630
(As if you have any relatives you can trust.)

64
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:40,030
(Jiang Niannian.)

65
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:42,310
(When will you really trust me?)

66
00:03:43,430 --> 00:03:44,270
Okay.

67
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:46,190
If he comes back,

68
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,960
