72
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,520
Niannian.

73
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,080
I need you to trust me.

74
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:06,680
I'll keep you safe.

75
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,920
(Ye Lang.)

76
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:11,800
(Can I really trust you?)

77
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:35,680
You were brave today,

78
00:04:37,430 --> 00:04:39,120
