79
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:42,110
Alright.

80
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,720
It's just a tiny cut.

81
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,510
Maybe it'll heal by tomorrow.

82
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,630
Even a slight wound

83
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,240
pains me to see it.

84
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:57,910
Niannian.

85
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,560
You must have

86
00:05:01,870 --> 00:05:03,040
