87
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:09,830
When I was little, living with my mom,

88
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:12,070
I was always bullied at school.

89
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,520
Later,

90
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,510
