96
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:43,260
I can't give you what you want.

97
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:51,560
ظآزJust To Meet You, you fell for meظآز

98
00:05:51,580 --> 00:05:56,070
ظآزJust to meet me, into my trap you fellظآز

99
00:06:03,250 --> 00:06:07,890
ظآزAre you real, or just a dream?ظآز

100
00:06:09,020 --> 00:06:12,130
ظآزHow did I fall so deep into this?ظآز

101
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:18,300
ظآزLike a chance encounter in plain sightظآز

102
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,070
