104
00:06:25,060 --> 00:06:28,130
ظآزYou're as beautiful as the moonlightظآز

105
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:35,090
ظآزI won't miss you or choose anyone elseظآز

106
00:06:40,620 --> 00:06:44,020
(Li &amp; Murong)

107
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,800
(Could the one who grabbed Xiaodi)

108
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,070
