109
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:52,750
That's Ye Lang.

110
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:54,360
Just an illegitimate son,

111
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,830
yet he holds the position.

112
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,830
Looks like you

113
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,870
have had a hard time in the Li family.

114
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,320
Even now,

115
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,520
