116
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:03,870
Feel bad for me?

117
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,800
Feeling bad for a guy

118
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,240
will bring me trouble.

119
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,630
What's this?

120
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:13,030
This is...

121
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,880
This is Water Lilies.

122
00:07:20,190 --> 00:07:21,160
Monet's Water Lilies.

123
00:07:21,510 --> 00:07:22,680
Is it real?

124
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:24,080
Sure, it's the Li family.

125
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,040
You even have an authentic Monet?

126
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,000
This painting

127
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:30,270
was a gift to my fianc├رe Xue.

128
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,390
It was given to me

129
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:33,230
by my brother's mom,

130
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:34,750
