133
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,040
- It...
- Fake?

134
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,000
Impossible.

135
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,870
Auntie Ye is such a great artist.

136
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:47,920
Why would she give me a fake?

137
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,430
The texture of the canvas

138
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:51,270
is smooth, with no visible grain.

139
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,430
But during Monet's period,

140
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:55,120
the canvas was coarse,

141
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:56,630
with visible texture.

142
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:58,110
This is clearly

143
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,950
a modern fake.

144
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,000
Li Hong.

145
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:03,240
Don't take this the wrong way,

146
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,360
