147
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,920
You're the true heir.

148
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,720
Ye Mei was just a mistress.

149
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:10,800
Would she give you this good thing?

150
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:13,000
