151
00:08:13,690 --> 00:08:14,580
You're overthinking it.

152
00:08:15,370 --> 00:08:16,600
Auntie Ye is very kind.

153
00:08:17,340 --> 00:08:18,680
No matter what others say,

154
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,680
