155
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:24,240
A woman willing to be "the other one"
will never be respected.

156
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,000
She's nothing special.

157
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:27,630
Ye Lang,

158
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:28,590
