161
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:36,200
(Brother, after all these years,)

162
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,750
(It's your turn to be looked down on.)

163
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:53,870
It looks like

164
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:55,080
she really knows her stuff.

165
00:08:57,300 --> 00:08:59,580
(Copy made at age 12.)

166
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:02,080
(A copy made at age 12.)

167
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,080
My future mother-in-law

168
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:14,080
was truly a genius.

169
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:15,870
At only twelve,

170
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:18,320
she could replicate Monet so convincingly.

171
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:19,970
No wonder

172
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,200
one original painting of hers is prized.

173
00:09:24,910 --> 00:09:25,750
I didn't expect

174
00:09:26,510 --> 00:09:28,320
