175
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:30,600
There's a lot I can do.

176
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:37,240
Father.

177
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,080
Why don't you go

178
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:39,960
see if Xue is ready?

179
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:42,390
Don't mess this up again.

180
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:44,240
Got it, I'll go now.

181
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:50,720
I'm Li Zhongtian.

182
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:52,910
Thank you all for attending

183
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:57,240
my son Li Hong and Murong Xue's
engagement ceremony.

184
00:09:58,120 --> 00:10:02,750
Here we'll also announce Ye Lang's marriage.

185
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,790
Jiang Niannian is like his mom.

186
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:07,630
A woman who brings no gain to the family

187
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,480
won't enter the Li family alive,

188
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:11,960
and won't be buried with them when dead.

189
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,920
Shut up!

190
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,440
Fine.

191
00:10:15,670 --> 00:10:16,720
I'll make an announcement.

192
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:20,910
Jiang Niannian and I

193
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:23,790
are officially engaged.

194
00:10:26,980 --> 00:10:27,820
Niannian.

195
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,390
I have a gift for you.

196
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:32,270
This is

197
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:33,510
Ye Mei's final painting?

198
00:10:34,390 --> 00:10:35,230
I heard

199
00:10:35,390 --> 00:10:37,910
it's already been valued
at 30 billion on the art market.

200
00:10:38,260 --> 00:10:39,110
30 billion?

201
00:10:39,110 --> 00:10:40,390
Before my mom passed,

202
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,320
she told me

203
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,440
this painting was for my wife.

204
00:10:45,380 --> 00:10:47,620
She wanted me to find someone
I could entrust my life to,

205
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:48,920
