206
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:51,000
but for happiness.

207
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,560
Niannian.

208
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,750
Will you accept it?

209
00:11:07,150 --> 00:11:08,670
I'm not forcing you today.

210
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:10,000
I just need your answer.

211
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:13,630
I only want the world to know my love.

212
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:15,960
If I do this,

213
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,510
