216
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,160
You're hurting me.

217
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:48,120
Sorry, Xue.

218
00:11:49,550 --> 00:11:51,150
It was meant to be our engagement party.

219
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,080
It's okay.

220
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:56,440
Even if no one supports us,

221
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,240
