222
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:00,630
Mm.

223
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,040
(Ye Lang.)

224
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:06,080
(Why do you always show up)

225
00:12:06,380 --> 00:12:08,180
(at the biggest moments and take all I have?)

226
00:12:28,010 --> 00:12:34,600
ظآزStitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red duskظآز

227
00:12:36,410 --> 00:12:42,620
ظآزYou return reborn,
seeing through all my cracksظآز

228
00:12:43,170 --> 00:12:50,170
ظآزThis tenderness, a trap or a gift?ظآز

229
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:53,390
ظآزStill, I'd wager my next life on itظآز

230
00:12:53,390 --> 00:12:58,390
ظآزJust for a moment to recognize you againظآز

231
00:12:58,390 --> 00:13:02,620
ظآزYou are the blazing light in my despairظآز

232
00:13:03,130 --> 00:13:07,060
ظآزLighting the edges of my frozen wingsظآز

233
00:13:07,110 --> 00:13:10,900
ظآزI burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fireظآز

234
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:16,650
ظآزBreaking free
from dead vines in the ashesظآز

235
00:13:16,650 --> 00:13:20,970
ظآزYou are the brightest star in the nightظآز

236
00:13:21,010 --> 00:13:24,830
ظآزAwakening my dormant fateظآز

237
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:29,330
ظآزFreeing me from this half-life prisonظآز

238
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:34,190
ظآزAs the bells shatter the pastظآز

239
00:13:34,590 --> 00:13:41,130
ظآزLife finds its way againظآز
